·aarch64架构:
golang、golang-devel、golang-help
·x86_64架构:
golang、golang-devel、golang-help
·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统（Host版）V10
·aarch64架构:
golang、golang-devel、golang-help
·x86_64架构:
golang、golang-devel、golang-help

